{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium wishlist page section that displays saved products in a grid. Use browser localStorage to store wishlist items. Show product image, title, price, variant selector, add to cart button, and remove from wishlist button for each item. Include empty state with message and shop now button when no items saved. Grid layout 2-4 columns with customizable spacing, colors, typography. Premium minimal design for luxury silk saree brand. All styling customizable from sidebar including padding, margins, button styles, card design.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
